r@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据 NME 独家透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>收养了一只无家可归的狗，并为泰国的动物慈善机构筹集了数千美元，从而获得了善待动物组织奖 (PETA Award)。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/liam-gallagher-and-john-squire-tour-3614825">利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）和约翰·斯奎尔（John Squire）在他们期待已久的合作中：“尘埃落定后，这是10首很棒的歌曲”</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-adopts-rescue-dog-buttons-from-thailand-3502001">去年从泰国的一个庇护所中收养了一只名为纽扣的狗</a>，因为她被前所有者“不够可爱”而被丛林遗弃。</p><p>加拉格尔（Gallagher）通过总部位于泰国的Happy Doggo Sanctuary找到了按钮，今年早些时候，该慈善机构的创始人Niall Harbison在应用程序中找到了Gallagher的名字时，讨论了他的震惊。巴顿飞行了近 6,000 英里（9,500 公里）抵达她在英国的新家。</p><p>收养她后不久，这位绿洲主唱透露，家里的新成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-doesnt-want-to-go-on-tour-anymore-since-adopting-thai-rescue-dog-3599581">让他不再想去巡演</a>——因为他宁愿呆在家里陪她——然后他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dog-home-owner-shares-touching-story-liam-gallaghers-work-help-save-animals-3785716">帮助筹集了 25,000 英镑来帮助其他狗泰国。</a></p><p>哈比森在 X/Twitter 上宣布了这一消息，并表示加拉格尔所做的努力“证明世界上并非一切都是坏事”。该慈善机构希望每月拯救 1,000 只狗。</p><p>现在，鉴于他的慈善工作以及他通过纽扣提高的意识，利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）被授予PETA享有声望的“打击右动物奖”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820476" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820476" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820476" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270.jpg" alt="PETA的“打击右动物奖”" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PETA-award@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3820476" class="wp-caption-text"> PETA的“打击右动物奖”。图片来源：媒体/善待动物组织</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6YvKJvohTN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556